    All Classes and Interfaces

    Class
    Description
    Calculator
    The Calculator class calculates the shipping costs of a package.
    CalculatorArea
    The CalculatorArea class represents the main interface for calculating shipping costs.
    CalculatorTest
    The CalculatorTest class contains tests for the Calculator class.
    DHBWArea
    The DHBWArea class represents a simple area above the calculator area.
    Importer
    The Importer class imports the package configurations from a csv file.
    ImporterTest
    The ImporterTest class contains the unit tests for the Importer class.
    Messages
    The Messages class represents a utility for displaying messages in the application.
    NotValidDimensionsException
    The NotValidDimensionsException class is an exception that is thrown when a package is not in valid dimensions.
    PackageCalculator
    The main application class for the PackageCalculator.
    PackageConfiguration
    The PackageConfiguration class contains a package with a price.
    PackageConfigurationPopup
    The PackageConfigurationPopup class represents a popup window for displaying package configurations.
    PackageConfigurationTest
    The PackageConfigurationTest class contains the unit tests for the PackageConfiguration class.
    PackageModel
    The PackageModel class contains the 3D model of the package.
    PackageModelArea
    The PackageModelArea class contains the 3D model of the package.
    Packet
    The Packet class contains the dimensions and weight of a packet.
    PacketTest
    The PacketTest class contains the unit tests for the Packet class.
    ToolbarArea
    The ToolbarArea class represents the toolbar in the application, providing buttons for various actions such as opening a project, creating a new file, and showing help information.
